<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-giJF6kkoqNQ00vy+HMDP7azOuL0xtbfIcaT9wjKHr8RbDVddVHyTfAAsrekwKmP1" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Amatic+SC:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> 
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Didact+Gothic&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> 
        <style>
            body {
                background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #e7c5a2, #e0be9a, #dab692, #d3af8a, #cda882, #c49f79, #bc9770, #b38e67, #a6815c, #987551, #8b6946, #7e5d3b);
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
                height: auto;
                color: #462300;
                font-family: 'Didact Gothic', sans-serif;
                font-size: 15pt;
                }
            h1 {
                font-family: 'Amatic SC', cursive;
                font-size: 50pt;
            }
        </style>
    <title>Cats and Facts</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container mt-5 mb-5 text-center">
            <h1>Cats and Facts</h1>  
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="container text-center">
            <div class="row text-center justify-content-center d-flex align-items-center">
                <div class="col-8">
                    <h3>Aqui estão seus gatos e fatos</h3>
                    <h6>(Estão em inglês, mas se você estiver utilizando o chrome, pode clicar com o botão direito do mouse e selecionar "traduzir para o português")</h6> <br>
                       
                    <% fatos.forEach(fato => { %>
                        <p> <%= fato.text %> </p> <br>
                    <% }) %>
    
                    <img src=" <%= gato.url %> " alt=""> <br>
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-dark my-5">Procurar outro gato e outro fato</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <footer>

    </footer>
    
</body>
</html>